        "text": "{\n  \"name\": \"Outro Usuário\",\n  \"email\": \"maria@wellme.com\",\n  \"password\": \"outrasenha1\"\n}"
      },
      "headers": [{ "name": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
      "description": "Espera 409 Conflict — DuplicateEmailException. Rode após já ter cadastrado maria@wellme.com."
